    "Yet again, Priscila is not always at these events-life circumstances get in the way.",
    "On these occasions, Ben has become well aware that he will be lucky to be handed a sandwich, as others rarely acknowledge his incapacity to identify what is on offer.",
    "He could ask, obviously.",
    "Yet repeated requests for reasonable adjustments to be acknowledged and implemented has become a hallmark of his day-to-day work, which he finds exhausting.",
